
Q Why Learn Python?
-> 1) Easy to code (begineer friendly)
   2) to many libraries for different fields.
   3) Large Scope :
    Artificial Intelligence, Machine Learning, Big data,
    Internet of Things,Data Science,Computer Automatic Design,
    Robotics,Automations,Designing, Graphical User Interface,
    Web Development, Hacking, and so on...
   4) One of the trending language so you can make good money.

Q What are the Feature or characteristics of python PL?
=>
1) Simplicity-: Userfriendly, readable, English type.
2) Freeware -: You don't need to pay a single penny to any
            organinization for using python.

           python.org //Non profitable organization (donation)
           java.com //commercial (money)

3) Open Source -: Source code open or available to all
           present on internet .

4) High level Language
5) It follows bot POP & OOPs Methodology.
6) Scripting Language: Python use Interpreter
7) Dynamically typed programming-:
        Static
     -> compile hone se pehle
     -> We need to specify the datatype of variable while
        declaring it in static types programming languages
        like c,c++, java

         Dynamic
      -> Run time prr decide hota hai interpreter ke dwara.
      -> We don't need to specify the datatype of  variable
         it automatically interpreted at the run time
         ( time taking ).

    c -> int a = 10 ;
         float b = 22.33;
         char c = 'A';

    python-> a = 10
             b = 222.33
             c = 'A'
             d = "lalit"

8) Platform Independent-:
    platform ( Operating System , windows,linux,macintosh)
    WORA (tagline) -: Write Once Run Anywhere.

9) Extensible (attach/extend) -> It provides us the ability
            to Integrate the code of any language with python.

10) Powerful Libraries -> Modules are compact with different
               number of rich  features and fuctions.

 Limitations of python:

 1) Slow language -: 1) Interpreted language
                     2) Dynamically typed.

 2) Not Good for  Mobile app development .
   facebook  flutter --Dart Programming.
    kotlin (google ) , React Native , java Mobile Edition

   kivy library hai python me karna ho to...

   i) Slow
   ii) Memory Management is not upto the mark

 Good program-> Less Resource (time & Space complexity)
                used to make our program faster and efficient.


